---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../../consts';

const chapters = [
  { year: 2011, title: 'Mobile payments as habit / 移动支付开始成为习惯', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2011-chapter-32-mobile-payments-as-habit/' },
  { year: 2012, title: 'Messaging super-apps / 通讯录变成生态入口', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2012-chapter-33-messaging-super-apps/' },
  { year: 2013, title: 'Data as exhaust / 数据成为生活的尾气', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2013-chapter-34-data-as-exhaust/' },
  { year: 2014, title: 'Recommendation systems / 推荐系统接管注意力', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2014-chapter-35-recommendation-systems/' },
  { year: 2015, title: 'Deep learning breaks through / 深度学习突破进入公共叙事', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2015-chapter-36-deep-learning-breaks-through/' },
  { year: 2016, title: 'The API economy / API 经济与平台化协作', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2016-chapter-37-the-api-economy/' },
  { year: 2017, title: 'Voice as interface / 语音开始成为界面', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2017-chapter-38-voice-as-interface/' },
  { year: 2018, title: 'Automation everywhere / 自动化进入生活深处', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2018-chapter-39-automation-everywhere/' },
  { year: 2019, title: 'Edge devices and cameras / 摄像头、边缘设备与被持续感知的世界', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2019-chapter-40-edge-devices-and-cameras/' },
  { year: 2020, title: 'Remote work at scale / 大规模远程化与平台社会定型', href: '/blog/volumes/vol-3-2011-2020/2020-chapter-41-remote-work-at-scale/' },
];
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead
      title={`${SITE_TITLE} · Volume III`}
      description="Volume III (2011–2020): the years when platforms, mobile systems, data, and algorithms reorganized ordinary life."
    />
    <style>
      .hero,
      .section {
        padding: 1.35rem 1.45rem;
        border-radius: 22px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(var(--line), 0.8);
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.76);
        box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
      }
      .hero + .section,
      .section + .section {
        margin-top: 1.2rem;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }
      .lead {
        max-width: 44rem;
      }
      .chapter-list {
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
      }
      .chapter-list li + li {
        margin-top: 0.45rem;
      }
      .chapter-list a {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .muted {
        color: rgb(var(--gray));
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Volume III / 第三卷</p>
        <h1>The Platform Age / 平台时代</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          This volume follows the years when the internet no longer merely entered daily life, but began to
          organize daily life through mobile systems, payment interfaces, recommendation logic, platform
          gateways, and data-driven coordination.
        </p>
        <p class="muted">
          这一卷写的是互联网不再只是进入生活，而开始通过移动系统、支付界面、推荐逻辑、平台入口和数据驱动协作，
          直接组织普通生活的阶段。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Editorial note / 编辑说明</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>如果第二卷写的是网络如何进入普通人的生活，那么第三卷写的就是：平台如何进一步接管普通人的生活组织方式。</strong>
          在这一卷里，入口变得更集中，行为变得更可测量，算法开始接管分发，平台开始深度嵌入支付、沟通、消费、协作与注意力结构。
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Included chapter entries / 已纳入章节入口</h2>
        <ol class="chapter-list">
          {chapters.map((chapter) => (
            <li>
              {chapter.href ? (
                <a href={chapter.href}>{chapter.year}: {chapter.title}</a>
              ) : (
                <span class="muted">{chapter.year}: {chapter.title}</span>
              )}
            </li>
          ))}
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <h2>Companion materials / 配套材料</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/volumes/vol-2-1996-2010/">Back to Volume II / 返回第二卷</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/01-method-volume/">Method volume / 方法卷</a></li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
